These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: drawing, board-games, writing, sudoku, fishing, singing, video-games
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, biathlon, cycling, parkour, skiing, volleyball
 1. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who's hobby is video-games##2
 2. the person who's hobby is board-games is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who's sport is parkour##2
 5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 6. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 7. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
 8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 9. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
10. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
11. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby   | sudoku | drawing | video-games | board-games    | writing | fishing   | singing    |
| Sport         | skiing  | baseball   | cycling | badminton | biathlon   | volleyball | parkour |

