 3. the person who's birthday is in september is the polish##1
 4. the german is on the left of the pakistani##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 6. the indian is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 7. the canadian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in november and the indian##2
 9. the canadian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
10. the dutch is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
