2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the fan of disco##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is between the fan of rock and the fan of classical##2
4. the fan of punk is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is cycling is in the middle##1
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the fan of classical##1
7. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
8. the person who's sport is rugby is the fan of house##1
9. the fan of metal is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
