4. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
5. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person playing monopoly##2
7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
8. the person playing canasta is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
